Sheep on the lamb sparks M-way chaosA SHEEP brought traffic to a standstill on a busy motorway today.The animal caused chaos when it escaped from a field and wandered on to a stretch of the M74.Drivers doing up to 70mph had to swerve or slam on the brakes to avoid the animal.The lone sheep was spotted in the motorway at junction 12 Millbank in South Lanarkshire.